WEBVTT

00:01:59.917 --> 00:02:01.643
because I'm obsessed with color.

00:02:01.667 --> 00:02:04.268
I teach a whole course on it
at my university.

00:02:04.292 --> 00:02:07.434
But my very first tattoo
was an all-black tattoo

00:02:07.458 --> 00:02:09.184
like Ötzi's.

00:02:09.208 --> 00:02:12.851
Yep, I did that clichéd thing
that young people do sometimes

00:02:12.875 --> 00:02:16.059
and I got a tattoo
in a language I can't even read.

00:02:16.083 --> 00:02:17.643
(Laughter)

00:02:17.667 --> 00:02:20.434
OK, but I was 19 years old,

00:02:20.458 --> 00:02:23.559
I had just returned
from my first trip overseas,

00:02:23.583 --> 00:02:25.976
I was in Japan in the mountains

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:28.476
meditating in Buddhist monasteries,

00:02:28.500 --> 00:02:30.768
and it was a really meaningful
experience to me,